    "description": "<p>Extremely close quarters warriors that are super fast and have phases where they cannot be hit at all. Used to get through enemy lines.</p>",
    "attacks": "<p><strong>Inflict Violence: Assassinate.</strong> Attack an adjacent enemy with Bravery (<strong>Hit on 5+</strong> if from Stealth).</p><p><strong>Gambits</strong> [[/r d8]]</p><p><strong>1-2:</strong> Rush &gt; Inflict Violence &gt; Rush</p><p><strong>3-4: Shadowstep [1]:</strong> Gain Stealth. If already in Stealth, <strong>teleport</strong> 4. &gt; Rush &gt; Inflict Violence</p><p><strong>5-6:</strong> Rush &gt; Inflict Violence &gt; <strong>Dual Wield [1]:</strong> Can only be used after an attack. Deal 1 Hit on the attacked fighter.</p><p><strong>7-8: Unrelenting Assault [3]:</strong> <strong>Teleport 3</strong> <em>three times,</em> inflicting violence after every teleport, ignoring Combo Breaker. If done from Stealth, stealth doesn't break until the end of all attacks. Must distribute equally: as much as possible, do not attack the same fighter more than once, unless there are none that the teleport can reach.</p>",
